{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-038", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 38.1", "sort_key": "038.001", "text_original": "上德不德，是以有德；", "text_normalized": "上德不德，是以有德；", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-002", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-038", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "老子 38.2", "sort_key": "038.002", "text_original": "下德不失德，是以無德。", "text_normalized": "下德不失德，是以無德。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-003", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-038", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "老子 38.3", "sort_key": "038.003", "text_original": "上德無為而無以為，下德為之而有以為。", "text_normalized": "上德無為而無以為，下德為之而有以為。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-004", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-038", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "老子 38.4", "sort_key": "038.004", "text_original": "上仁為之而無以為，上義為之而有以為。", "text_normalized": "上仁為之而無以為，上義為之而有以為。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-005", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-038", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "老子 38.5", "sort_key": "038.005", "text_original": "上禮為之而莫之應，則攘臂而扔之。", "text_normalized": "上禮為之而莫之應，則攘臂而扔之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-006", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-038", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "老子 38.6", "sort_key": "038.006", "text_original": "故失道而後德，失德而後仁，失仁而後義，失義而後禮。", "text_normalized": "故失道而後德，失德而後仁，失仁而後義，失義而後禮。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-007", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-038", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "老子 38.7", "sort_key": "038.007", "text_original": "夫禮者，忠信之薄，而亂之首。", "text_normalized": "夫禮者，忠信之薄，而亂之首。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-008", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-038", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "老子 38.8", "sort_key": "038.008", "text_original": "前識者，道之華，而愚之始。", "text_normalized": "前識者，道之華，而愚之始。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-009", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-038", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "老子 38.9", "sort_key": "038.009", "text_original": "是以大丈夫處其厚，不居其薄；", "text_normalized": "是以大丈夫處其厚，不居其薄；", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-010", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-038", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "老子 38.10", "sort_key": "038.010", "text_original": "處其實，不居其華。", "text_normalized": "處其實，不居其華。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-011", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-038", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-038__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "老子 38.11", "sort_key": "038.011", "text_original": "故去彼取此。", "text_normalized": "故去彼取此。", "notes": ""}
